data.description: 15 acres and a stunning one-story brick home that has been impeccably maintained for 16 years in Alice, TX. This peaceful oasis offers a split bedroom floor plan with 3 spacious bedrooms, 2.5 baths, and a flex room that can be used however you wish. The inverted ceiling throughout the home gives it an open and airy feel, and you will love the ceramic tile that runs throughout. The open concept kitchen with a breakfast nook and formal dining area is perfect for entertaining guests. The kitchen has granite countertops and an island, providing ample space to prepare meals. Generous sized living room and a spacious laundry room features a storage closet. The detached 2-car bricked carport comes complete with a storage, large metal workshop barn with electrical and 2 overhead doors. Horse stable that features 16 stalls with an unfinished living quarter, a second horse barn with 2 stalls, hot walker and a round pin. Do not miss out on this one!
